Class SafeSortedMap.SkipNode

java.lang.Object
com.tangosol.util.SafeSortedMap.SkipNode
Direct Known Subclasses:
SafeSortedMap.IndexNode
Enclosing class:
SafeSortedMap
protected static class SafeSortedMap.SkipNode extends Object
SkipNode is an entry or index node in the lattice for a SafeSortedMap's representation.
